  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<p>Discover Europe’s most spectacular destinations on an Inghams escorted tour. We offer a wide range of tours across the continent from wine tasting in <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a> to speeding past <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland’s</a> dramatic scenery on a rail tour. Or why not explore <a data-udi="umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54" href="/{localLink:umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54}" title="Norway">Norway’s</a> spectacular fjords or the beautiful towns on the <a data-udi="umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47}" title="Amalfi Coast">Amalfi Coast</a>? Perhaps venture a little further and discover the many highlights of Canada on our new tours exploring this diverse and spectacular country. Each of our tours has been carefully crafted to create itineraries that explore the very best these countries have to offer. </p>
<p>Choosing an escorted tour gives you the freedom to discover destinations without having to worry about the details. Our expert tour leaders will take care of every element and their passion and local knowledge will bring the journey to life. Group sizes on an Inghams escorted tour are kept to a minimum meaning you’ll get a more personal experience and we’ve included as much as possible in the price so you won’t have any unexpected expenses when you’re away.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Take a look at our complete range of Escorted Tours below</strong></h2>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Italy<br />Neapolitan Splendours</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/neapolitan-splendours-escorted-tour"><strong><img src="/media/13072514/shutterstock_759048709.jpg" alt="Neapolitan Splendours" data-udi="umb://document/1b38a4293ff04cc8b2dd360a57a538d8" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>8 days from £1,395 per person</strong></p>
<p>Explore the dramatic terrain of the Neapolitan Coast with this fantastic tour. From Sorrento to glamorous Capri, the wonders of Campania are not to be missed.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/neapolitan-splendours-escorted-tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Italy<br />Grand Tour of Sicily</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/grand-tour-of-sicily-escorted-tour"><strong><img src="/media/13072528/adobestock_34752426.jpeg" alt="Grand Tour of Sicily" data-udi="umb://document/b037a20c14a3421ba33b32859c9e3344" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>8 days from £1,495 per person</strong></p>
<p>This small group tour will take you on a journey around the island, through Sicily's ancient towns, stunning archaeological sites and Europe’s largest volcano.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/grand-tour-of-sicily-escorted-tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Italy<br />Best of Puglia &amp; Basilicata</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/best-of-puglia-basilicata-escorted-tour"><strong><img src="/media/13072537/adobestock_87586758.jpeg" alt="Best of Puglia" data-udi="umb://document/d0c28188245b40a396dd64fb346dffcd" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>8 days from £1,149 per person</strong></p>
<p>Puglia is known for its whitewashed towns and beautiful coast. Visit the Trulli houses of Alberobello, the olive groves of Ostuni and vibrant town of Otranto.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/best-of-puglia-basilicata-escorted-tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Switzerland<br />Swiss Classic Tour</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-switzerland/swiss-classic-escorted-tour"><strong><img src="/media/13074704/bernina_express_sommer.jpg" alt="Swiss Classic Tour" data-udi="umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>10 days from £2,329 per person</strong></p>
<p>Experience two of the most spectacular panoramic journeys in the world on the Bernina and Glacier Express. Enjoy the extraordinary landscape and picturesque towns.</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-switzerland/swiss-classic-escorted-tour">Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Canada<br />Canadian Contrasts</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/canadian-contrasts-escorted-tour"><strong><img src="/media/13079833/banff-national-park-2.jpg" alt="Banff National Park" data-udi="umb://media/2bf76fd1ea364c689e58def6d33c5623" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>15 days from £3,049 per person</strong></p>
<p>Discover the highlights of Canada on this two-week tour. Starting from the colonial towns of Quebec and ending in the unspoiled frontiers of British Columbia.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/canadian-contrasts-escorted-tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Canada<br />Eastern Journey</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/eastern-journey-escorted-tour"><strong><img src="/media/13079861/niagara-falls.jpg" alt="Niagra Falls" data-udi="umb://media/2c466872d32841129abec1c5cb6039a6" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>8 days from £1,699 per person</strong></p>
<p>Spend a week travelling along Canada's eastern coast and discover Maritime heritage, the thundering Niagara Falls, historic towns and a vibrant urban scene.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/tours-and-multi-centre-holidays/holiday-types/escorted-tours"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Canada<br />Western Journey</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/western-journey-escorted-tour"><strong><img src="/media/13079852/banff-national-park-moraine-lake.jpg" alt="Banff National Park" data-udi="umb://media/5a4fa5debdc449ff879592485cd6c14b" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>8 days from £1,919 per person</strong></p>
<p>Western Canada is peppered with spectacular National Parks, mountain resorts and bustling cities. Experience these on a journey from Calgary to Vancouver.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/western-journey-escorted-tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Iceland<br />Wonders of Iceland</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/wonders-of-iceland-escorted-tour"><strong><img src="/media/13074608/whale-watching-husavik-humpback-blowing-3.jpg" alt="Wonders" data-udi="umb://document/034b02ad431f4de8b15f328605d821cb" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>9 days from £2,799 per person</strong></p>
<p>This tour showcases the nature, culture and history that Iceland has to offer including whale watching, boat trips, hot springs and national parks.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/wonders-of-iceland-escorted-tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Iceland<br />Summer Explorer</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/iceland-s-summer-explorer-escorted-tour"><strong><img src="/media/13074604/seljalandsfoss-1751463_1920-1.jpg" alt="Iceland's Summer Explorer" data-udi="umb://document/e182536f884b4cf5bb49714367500792" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>9 days from £2,499 per person</strong></p>
<p>Start in Reykjavík before completing the Iceland Ring Road and all the sights along the way including the famous Golden Circle and Vatnajokull National Park.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/iceland-s-summer-explorer-escorted-tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Iceland<br />Volcanoes &amp; Glaciers</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/land-of-volcanoes-and-glaciers-escorted-tour"><strong><img src="/media/13074613/eyjafjallajoekull-2.jpg" alt="Land of Volcanoes and Glaciers" data-udi="umb://document/034b02ad431f4de8b15f328605d821cb" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>6 days from £1,449 per person</strong></p>
<p>Iceland really is the land of Volcanoes and Glaciers and this insightful tour is ideal for showcasing the country's amazing natural wonders.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/land-of-volcanoes-and-glaciers-escorted-tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br /><br /></p>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Norway<br />Highlights of the Fjords</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/highlights-of-the-fjords"><strong><img src="/media/13074702/geiranger-more-og-romsdal-072005-99-3027.jpg" alt="Highlights of the Fjords" data-udi="umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>12 days from £1,979 per person</strong></p>
<p>An excellent introduction to Norway for those wishing to see the spectacular fjords, mountains, glaciers and lakes in four contrasting destinations.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/highlights-of-the-fjords"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a name="backtotop"></a>Norway<br />Bergen to Oslo</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/bergen-to-oslo-fjord-experience"><strong><img src="/media/13074703/norway_journey_fjords_main.jpg" alt="Bergen to Oslo" data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" /></strong></a></p>
<p><strong>7 days from £1,299 per person</strong></p>
<p>Take a journey through the Fjords and travel on panoramic trains, ferries and railways to really experience the breath-taking nature that Norway has to offer.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/bergen-to-oslo-fjord-experience"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
